pha with straight bar; lunate epsilon and sigma; uncial mu and omega; rhomboid omicron, theta and phi.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
